headline: Cybersecurity Innovation – Fireside Chat with Fortinet COO John Whittle
summary: TechEdge hosted a fireside chat with Fortinet Chief Operating Officer John Whittle to talk about the company’s global presence, how they’ve secured over half a million organizations worldwide and their 2024 financial results. headline: 5 Top-Ranked Stocks Poised for an Earnings Beat
summary: Top-ranked stocks Tenet Healthcare (THC), Fortinet (FTNT), Lyft (LYFT), Garmin (GRMN) and Doximity (DOCS) are likely to beat on the bottom line in their upcoming releases.
